data.description: SELLER TO CONTRIBUTE $10,000 TO BUYERS CLOSING COSTS!!! Experience luxury living in this exquisite home located in the highly coveted PROSPER ISD!! Indulge in outdoor entertainment with an upgraded kitchen, built-in grill, living area, and fire pit equipped with an audio system and TV. Enjoy the savings of a solar system that nearly covers all monthly electricity expenses. The open kitchen floor plan, gas fireplace, and community pool nearby create a perfect blend of comfort and style. NORTH FACING home situated right across the road from the new Omni Resort and Fields Ranch golf course. This residence is nestled in one of the metroplex's most developing areas, offering a prime location for transportation next to DNT for an easy commute. With abundant shopping and dining options nearby, this beautifully maintained dream home will not last long.
